_sText:
I made this map for the nostaglia of beating bhop badges after practicing each stage a bunch. 

It contains a 8 stages which takes all from 5 seconds to 40 seconds to beat, I removed some super fishy jumps in longer stages so that it wouldn't be too cancerous.  

I didn't intend to release it originally and didn't bother making the map look good, and now it's too late to do any drastic changes to the layout.
